title: EP#33 - The Woman on the Bridge

description:
Terror is in store for a group of young friends when they investigate a chilling legend surrounding an old train bridge. Written by Spider One. Featuring Spider One as narrator and Steve, Krsy Fox as The Witch, and Riley Cummings as Pete. **Join our official Patreon and support the show! Get ad-free episodes, shout-outs, and more. Click the link to join https://www.patreon.com/bleedersdiegest To haunt us on social media click here https://linktr.ee/bleedersdiegest
